1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,647
Clinical presentation spans a broad spectrum.

2
00:00:02,647 --> 00:00:05,734
Chest pain — mimicking ACS — occurs

3
00:00:05,734 --> 00:00:08,822
in 82 to 95 percent of patients.

4
00:00:08,822 --> 00:00:11,468
Dyspnea affects 19 to 49 percent.

5
00:00:11,468 --> 00:00:14,556
In 75 percent of cases, the course

6
00:00:14,556 --> 00:00:17,203
is uncomplicated with near-zero in-hospital mortality.

7
00:00:17,203 --> 00:00:20,290
However, the remaining 25 percent present with

8
00:00:20,290 --> 00:00:23,378
LVEF below 50 percent, ventricular arrhythmias, or

9
00:00:23,378 --> 00:00:26,466
acute heart failure — carrying in-hospital mortality

10
00:00:26,466 --> 00:00:29,553
up to 12 percent and 15 percent

11
00:00:29,553 --> 00:00:32,200
mortality or transplant at five years.
